local MessageBox = require "actions/MessageBox" local Animate = require "actions/Animate" local Serial = require "actions/Serial" local Do = require "actions/Do"
return function(self) if GameState:hasItem("Key Card") then GameState:setFlag(self) return Serial { MessageBox { message = "Computer: Access granted.", textSpeed = 4, blocking = true, sfx = "levelup"}, self.scene.objectLookup.Door:open(), Do(function() self.scene.player.state = "idledown" end) } else return Serial { MessageBox { message = "Computer: Keycard required.", textSpeed = 4, blocking = true, sfx = "error"}, Animate(self.scene.player.sprite, "thinking"), MessageBox { message = "Sally: Hmmm... {p70}we'll need to find another way in.", blocking = true}, Do(function() self.scene.player.state = "idledown" end) } end end
